1062     public static Match CompoundStatement(CmajorLexer& lexer, ParsingContext* ctx)
1063     {
1064         #if (DEBUG)
1065             Span debugSpan;
1066             bool writeToLog = lexer.Log() != null;
1067             if (writeToLog)
1068             {
1069                 debugSpan = lexer.GetSpan();
1070                 System.Lex.WriteBeginRuleToLog(lexer, u"CompoundStatement");
1071             }
1072         #endif
1073         UniquePtr<CompoundStatementNode> compoundStatement;
1074         UniquePtr<StatementNode> stmt;
1075         Match match(false);
1076         Match* parentMatch0 = &match;
1077         {
1078             Match match(false);
1079             Match* parentMatch1 = &match;
1080             {
1081                 Match match(false);

1083                 {
1084                     long pos = lexer.GetPos();
1085                     Span span = lexer.GetSpan();
1086                     Match match(false);
1087                     if (*lexer == LBRACE)
1088                     {
1089                         ++lexer;
1090                         match.hit = true;
1091                     }
1092                     if (match.hit)
1093                     {
1094                         compoundStatement.Reset(new CompoundStatementNode(span));
1095                         compoundStatement->SetBeginBraceSpan(span);
1096                     }
1097                     *parentMatch2 = match;
1098                 }
1099                 *parentMatch1 = match;
1100             }
1101             if (match.hit)
1102             {
1103                 Match match(false);
1104                 Match* parentMatch3 = &match;
1105                 {
1106                     Match match(true);
1107                     Match* parentMatch4 = &match;
1108                     {
1109                         while (true)
1110                         {
1111                             long save = lexer.GetPos();
1112                             {
1113                                 Match match(false);
1114                                 Match* parentMatch5 = &match;
1115                                 {
1116                                     Match match(false);
1117                                     Match* parentMatch6 = &match;
1118                                     {
1119                                         long pos = lexer.GetPos();
1120                                         Match match = StatementParser.Statement(lexer, ctx);
1121                                         stmt.Reset(cast<StatementNode*>(match.value));
1122                                         if (match.hit)
1123                                         {
1124                                             compoundStatement->AddStatement(stmt.Release());
1125                                         }
1126                                         *parentMatch6 = match;
1127                                     }
1128                                     *parentMatch5 = match;
1129                                 }
1130                                 if (match.hit)
1131                                 {
1132                                     *parentMatch4 = match;
1133                                 }
1134                                 else
1135                                 {
1136                                     lexer.SetPos(save);
1137                                     break;
1138                                 }
1139                             }
1140                         }
1141                     }
1142                     *parentMatch3 = match;
1143                 }
